high_descs: Turn around and take two steps, then turn left and take one step, then turn right to face the table.
Pick up the yellow knife near the bread on the table.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink, turn the faucet on for three seconds, then turn the faucet off and pick up the knife.
Turn around and take two steps, then turn right to face the table.
Put the knife down on the table directly to the left of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Wash the knife in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, move past the table on your left, move around to face the side of the table to your left, facing the side of the knife.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn around, bring the knife to the sink.
Wash the knife in the sink.
Turn around, bring the cleaned knife to the center of the long table on your right.
Stand the knife on the table, to the left of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Stand a washed knife on the table.

high_descs: Put the knife down on the table
anns.task_desc: Wash a knife and put it back
